snippet.title: The Chant - Reel 3 - Hannah’s Footsteps
snippet.description:
In our third and final #TheChant Reel feature before launch on November 3rd, Hannah’s brother Thomas continues on his search to find her, discovering some intriguing revelations about our idyllic little island in the Pacific Northwest.

Get ready to dive into the spiritual nightmare of The Chant when it launches November 3rd, 2022 on PC, PS5 and Xbox Series. Pre-order your copy now at https://www.thechant.com and follow on social for more info:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheChantGame
Facebook: https://facebook.com/TheChantGame
Instagram: https://instagram.com/thechantgame
Official Website: https://www.thechant.com

#TheChant #HorrorGame #PrimeMatter #horrorgaming
